description: Spectacular waterfront 1 BR + office/den, 1.5 BA! Flawless floorplan! Full service luxury living with unobstructed Seaport & water views, 1 garage parking space with valet option & private direct access balcony. Lavish, contemporary entertaining space with expansive living room featuring Italian wide plank walnut floors & brilliant floor-to-ceiling windows. Gourmet kitchen with a stylish combination of white & wooden custom cabinetry that complement the marble countertops & waterfall island. Large primary suite with Carrara marble bathroom and spacious double vanity. Large additional office/den (or guest bedroom), laundry in-unit & ample storage. Constructed in 2019, 24-hour concierge/valet, gym, private resident’s lounge with gas fireplace, kitchen & adjoining terrace with grill, fire pit, virtual golf studio & dog spa. Photos are virtually staged as we await the installation of custom ordered finishes. Seller welcomes offers with requests for buyer concessions. Outstanding home!
